{"tid":2149411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湖南邵陽取締電單車惹民憤 數千民眾抗議政府即撤令","createTime":"2020-08-10T11:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T06:08:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0d6a0679a6855a8d211ebfe7aaa67862f55d96","tid":2149411,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/6OXKYXUXNK4KIT7JNQTYJ2UVDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2F6OXKYXUXNK4KIT7JNQTYJ2UVDE%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=656557f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2F6OXKYXUXNK4KIT7JNQTYJ2UVDE%2F&h=5840c3b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/6OXKYXUXNK4KIT7JNQTYJ2UVDE/</a><br />\n<br />\n官逼自然會引民反。湖南省邵陽市正進行取締電動車行動，單車、電單車同樣受影響。在一星期的取締行動中，據報已查扣數以千計的電動車，引發當地市民強烈不滿。上周五（7日）終爆發衝突，數千民眾集體到政府門前抗議時，有示威者堵塞官員的車輛及追打交警，多人抗議民眾被捕。邵陽當局當天宣佈暫停取締行動。"},{"pid":"9ccf965f5c61194334600cecadd9828d2cf91c10","tid":2149411,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b04292a18fcfbde86160ce890fa35a29e9ab00a","tid":2149411,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.